snippet.textDisplay: Jaclyn, I don’t ever comment on videos but I’m a long time subscriber and have watched you go through life on the internet which clearly isn’t easy. I couldn’t imagine having the world see me at my lows because it’s hard to pick yourself up sometimes but when thousands of people are trying to kick you back down, it probably feels impossible. I love seeing you continue to fight and work hard to bring your dreams to life, despite everything you’ve been through. Just know that there are so many of us rooting and supporting you. This pallet is a work of freaking art. You put your heart and soul into it and it shows and I can’t wait to get my hands on it! I actually haven’t ever really been into eye shadow until I saw your first pallet and now this one. They inspire me to dive into that part of make up that I’ve never really had interest in. Thank you for everything you do. Thank you for your hard work and dedication. Thank you for not quitting and giving up when so many other people would of. All of us, your true friends and subscribers, are so proud and excited for this launch! Love handles and all, we love you Jaclyn!!
